summary: "Evil in general does not sleep, and therefore doesn't see why anyone else should. But Crowley liked sleep, it was one of the...
body:
“Evil in general does not sleep, and therefore doesn’t see why anyone else should. But Crowley liked sleep, it was one of the pleasures of the world. (…) He’d slept through mist of the nineteenth century for example. Not because he needed to, simply because he enjoyed it.”

- Good Omens

Crowley being a cinamonroll pt 2

summary: One thing I’m confused about my dudes...were Time Lords not allowed to leave Gallifrey? Or were they all forced to fight in the...
body:
One thing I’m confused about my dudes…were Time Lords not allowed to leave Gallifrey? Or were they all forced to fight in the war? Was there not ONE Time Lord out of 2.42 billion, not even a mad one (except the master) that ditched the war out of fear? I’ve always wondered if there was another one out there but the doctor just hasn’t found them yet.

What if he finds another sane Time Lord but they die anyway? :D

summary:
"He'd been an angel once. He hadn't meant to Fall. He'd just hung around with the wrong people."
- Good Omens
Now look at this...
body:
“He’d been an angel once. He hadn’t meant to Fall. He’d just hung around with the wrong people.”

- Good Omens

Now look at this quote very closely. Keep in mind that it was said right after Crowley was honoured with mission of handling Antichrust aka the most important thing for a demon to do because he was so good at beeing demon on Earth. Keep in mind that he was sad, angry and devastated because he liked being on Earth and didn’t want Armageddon. And that he wouldn’t be happy with living in endless Hell even though he’s a deamon.

Keeping it all in mind, tell me that Crowley isn’t an ultimate cinamonroll.

summary: Good Omens - שד ומלאך יוצאים להציל את העולם
title: Good Omens - שד ומלאך יוצאים להציל את העולם
body:
Good Omens – שד ומלאך יוצאים להציל את העולם

במהלך כנס קומיקון בניו-יורק נחשף הטריילר הראשון לסדרת האדפטציה החדשה והמצחיקה Good Omens

כנס קומיקון של ניו-יורק הוכיח השנה שכנס הגיקים השנתי של התפוח הגדול הוא לא כנס דרג ב’ לכנס בעל אותו השם מסן דייגו, וזה בעיקר תודות לטריילרים חמים של “אקווה מן“, “דרדוויל” (שמתרחשת בניו-יורק) וכעת, החשיפה של הסדרה החדשה והמעניינת Good Omens.

Good Omens היא סדרת טלוויזיה בריטית המבוססת על הספר בעל אותו השם…
